high_descs: Turn right and walk around the kitchen island, then veer left to the coffee maker on the counter to the left of the sink.
Take the mug out of the coffee maker.
Wash the mug in the sink.
Place the mug back in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean cup in a coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn around to head to the coffee machine next to the sink.
Take the mug from the coffee machine.
Walk to the sink on the right.
Rinse the mug in the sink, removing it again.
Turn left to walk to the coffee machine.
Put the mug back on the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a mug from the coffee machine to put back.

high_descs: Turn around, go across the room, turn left and go to the coffee maker on the right.
Pick up the cup on the coffee maker.
Turn right and go to the sink.
Put the cup in the sink, rinse it off and pick it back up.
Turn left and go back to the coffee maker.
Put the cup on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a rinsed cup on the coffee maker.
